      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "PRINCE TOMMY (2) was fast into stride from box four to score two back (24.63) then jumped from the same draw last time but got further back when 5th at this track (25.22). Won at his only start from this box. Should be very hard to beat this time. TRALAERO (1) copped a check in the run and finished a well held 32 lengths eighth (31.54) last time in a Special conditions H at Sandown over 515m. Worth following up. PURE BLUE (3) has a strong record this track and trip with two wins and three placings from six starts. Was out of the placings last time (20.11) at this track in a Grade 5, finishing fifth and beaten 6 lengths. Can feature in the finish. HOW HIGH (6) collected a minor prize last start out of the same box - must be considered.",
